<h3><strong>Arshad Warsi on Asur Season 5</strong></h3>

<p>In the same interview, the Hulchul actor spilled the beans about <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/exclusives/exclusive-video-barun-sobti-shares-major-update-on-asur-3-sheds-light-on-how-show-changed-perception-about-him-1390643">Asur Season 3</a> plans. Arshad said that since the series needs intense research, the writers are taking time to perfect it. Having said that, they are working on it and have written the third season. &ldquo;It is very interesting. They&rsquo;re now working on the dates, and hopefully we will start shooting soon,&rdquo; revealed the actor who plays Dhananjay Rajpoot (DJ) in the psychological crime thriller TV series.</p>

