<p style="text-align: justify;">With the shoot now slated to conclude in June and post-production stretching well into the rear end of the year, industry insiders suggest that a January (Republic Day) or February (Valentine&#39;s Day) 2027 release is now likely if not almost certain. While the delay extends the wait, it also underlines the makers&rsquo; intent to deliver a visually and technically grand cinematic experience.</p>
