<p>Written by Vishal Bhardwaj and Rohan Narula, O&rsquo; Romeo is slated for release on February 13, 2026, just a day ahead of Valentine&rsquo;s Day.</p>

<p><strong>Shahid Kapoor&rsquo;s work front</strong></p>

<p>Shahid Kapoor last appeared in a lead role in the film Deva. Directed by Rosshan Andrrews, the action thriller follows the story of ACP Dev Ambre, a violent young cop who undergoes a drastic personality change after losing his memory in an accident and is forced to reinvestigate the death of a fellow police officer.</p>

