<p>A source close to the development reveals, &ldquo;This ambitious project is based on a strong story that was originally written for Allu Arjun and has generated tremendous excitement among fans and the film fraternity. It is expected to blend powerful storytelling with grand visuals, redefining the mythological genre for a pan-Indian and global audience. The film is scheduled to go on floors in February 2027. Before that, Allu Arjun is expected to complete the shoot and release of Atlee&rsquo;s film.&rdquo;</p>

<p>The <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/south/exclusive-allu-arjuns-film-with-trivikram-to-go-on-floors-in-2025-actor-to-do-one-more-movie-after-pushpa-2-1242331">Allu Arjun&ndash;Trivikram</a> combination has always been a treat for audiences, and fans of both the actor and the director are eagerly awaiting this much-talked-about project.</p>

