<p>(We started shooting early in the morning, by 12-1 o&#39;clock some people started coming, they started coming while watching the pictures from Gaiety Galaxy. Shooting was going on, Rani Mukherjee is here, Chandu Bhai&hellip; oh this is Chandu Bhai. Within no time, by lunch break 1000-2000 people had come, the entire security had become a nightmare. As soon as I got up, Shaad locked me inside the make-up van. Everyone started shouting Chandu Bhai Chandu Bhai&hellip;)</p>

