<p>(So I entered smoking a cigarette, like a gangster, sitting on a chair with my feet on the table and my slippers on the table. At the end of the day, he said, &quot;What a tremendous audition. I have never seen an audition like this.&quot; Finally, he said, &quot;You&#39;re doing my film.&rdquo;)&nbsp;</p>

