<p><strong>More about Cocktail</strong></p>

<p>For those unaware, Cocktail is a romantic comedy that was released in 2012. The film, starring Saif Ali Khan in the lead role, featured Deepika Padukone and Diana Penty as co-leads.</p>

<p>The first installment told a contemporary love triangle involving Gautam Kapoor, Veronica Melaney, and Meera Sahni, exploring the intersecting themes of romance and friendship. Directed by Homi Adajania himself, the film was based on a story written by Imtiaz Ali and Sajid Ali.</p>

