<p>Haiwaan is an upcoming Hindi-language movie starring Akshay Kumar and <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/cinema/my-girlfriend-is-two-years-younger-than-you-soha-ali-khan-recalls-how-saif-ali-khan-first-introduced-kareena-to-her-1396036">Saif Ali Khan</a> in the lead roles. Directed by Priyadarshan, the film is touted to be an adaptation of Mohanlal&rsquo;s 2016 thriller Oppam.</p>

