<p>When asked if Ssunita Ahuja now oversees Govinda&rsquo;s work, he said, &ldquo;Pata nai woh toh mujhe. Mein toh bhola bhaiya, woh toh kabhi alag hoge nai.&rdquo; (I don&rsquo;t know about that. I&rsquo;ve always known them together; they were never separate.)</p>

