<p><strong>Here&rsquo;s what everyone&rsquo;s asking: Are Govinda and Sunita divorcing?</strong></p>

<p>Nihalani&rsquo;s take was firm: The buzz doesn&rsquo;t match what he has seen. He stressed friendship and partnership, not separation.</p>

