<p>When asked about the situation at the hospital after Divya Bharti&rsquo;s sudden fall in 1993, Nihalani said she was alone when she was brought in. &ldquo;Akeli bichari thi tab tak koi nai tha,&rdquo; (She was all alone, by that time no one was there), he revealed. He added that by the time he reached, no one from her family had arrived. &ldquo;Tab tak kisiko nai tha, jab tak aaya jab mujhe maalum padaa immediately I rushed to the hospital,&rdquo; he said. (Till then, no one had come. As soon as I found out, I immediately rushed to the hospital.)</p>

<p><strong>Here&rsquo;s what Nihalani remembers about working with her</strong></p>

<p><a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/exclusives/union-budget-2021-exclusive-pahlaj-nihalani-feels-gst-film-industry-should-be-waived-next-3-years-605188">Pahlaj Nihalani</a> also shared memories from the Shola Aur Shabnam sets. He recalled how professional and dedicated Divya was despite injuries. &ldquo;She has worked pura, per mein nail ghus gaya tha uske. Raat ke 3 baje the aur subah 6 baje gaane ke liye tayyar hui, maine bola shooting cancel kardi maine,&rdquo; (She kept working, a nail had pierced her foot. It was 3 a.m. at night, and by 6 a.m. she was ready for a song shoot. I told her the shooting was cancelled.) he shared.</p>

<p>The filmmaker shared a&nbsp;moment to show how dedicated Divya Bharti was when she&nbsp;surprised him and his wife. &ldquo;Mein soya tha ki subah cancel hain, fir bhi room mein aayi, mera housekeeping se darwaza khola aake beth gayi mere chest pe ki utho. Meri wife boli ye kaun hain. Matlab mein aur wife dono soye hain aake mere peth pe aake baith gayi.&rdquo; (I was asleep since the morning shoot was cancelled, but still she came into my room, got the door opened through housekeeping, and sat on my chest saying &lsquo;wake up&rsquo;. My wife asked, &quot;Who is this girl? Both my wife and I were sleeping, and she came and sat on my stomach.&quot;&nbsp;Nihalani said.</p>

<p>Even decades later, Divya Bharti continues to be remembered as one of the most talented young actresses of her time. Nihalani&rsquo;s memories shed light on her dedication, charm, and the tragic loneliness of her final moments.</p>
