<p>And now, come 2025, Pinkvilla has exclusively learnt that Khosla Ka Ghosla 2 is in the making and is set to go on floors towards the end of year. According to sources close to the development, Umesh Bist and team have cracked as script that&rsquo;s an extension of the Khosla Ka Ghosla world. &ldquo;Khosla Ka Ghosla 2 script is locked and presently in the casting stage. The team is aiming to start by November this year, for a 2026 release. Much like the first part, this one too is an outright comic entertainer,&rdquo; revealed a source.</p>

